title: New MacOS 10.14 features appear to leak ahead of WWDC 2018
content: It wouldn't be a huge annual trade show without a few appetite-whetting leaks.Just a few short days before Apple's Worldwide Developer's Conference (WWDC) kicks off on June 4, an apparent leaks points to some incoming MacOS updates.
